## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Scope

This change request covers the **Injector** module of the Kiro SDLC Agent VS Code extension. The Injector is responsible for copying pre-packaged resource files from the extension’s bundled resources directory into the user’s workspace.

### 1.2 Out of Scope

* UI for indexer language selection (KSA-4)
* Auto-detection of runtime environment (KSA-5)
* Extension activation and command registration (KSA-2)

## 2. Business Requirements

### 2.2 User Stories

| # | Story | Priority |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Inject all SDLC resources | MUST HAVE |
| 2 | Selectively inject components | SHOULD HAVE |
| 3 | Skip excluded directories | MUST HAVE |
| 4 | Filtered copy for indexer | MUST HAVE |
| 5 | Check component status | SHOULD HAVE |

